## Beads (Task Management)

This project uses [beads](https://github.com/steveyegge/beads) for task tracking.

```bash
bd ready                    # Show tasks ready to work on
bd ready --assignee=ralph   # Show tasks assigned to Ralph
bd list --status=in_progress # What's being worked on
bd update <id> --status in_progress  # Claim a task
bd close <id>               # Complete a task
bd comment <id> "note"      # Add a comment
```

## Ralph (Autonomous Loop)

```bash
./ralph.sh 10               # Run 10 iterations (standalone)
./ralph-dashboard.sh 10     # Run 10 iterations (with dashboard monitoring)
./ralph-schedule.sh "11pm" . 50  # Schedule 50 iterations at 11pm
```

